<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="92000000t" end="137600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">「約定的夢幻島 S2」</p>
<p begin="159200000t" end="198000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">(回想起來了　回想起來了)</p>
<p begin="198800000t" end="238000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">(在那一眨眼間的絕望感覺)</p>
<p begin="238800000t" end="278000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">(即使醒來了　仍然在夢中)</p>
<p begin="278800000t" end="321590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">(夢見我們剎那光輝的故事)</p>
<p begin="323600000t" end="362800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">(時鐘的秒針)</p>
<p begin="363600000t" end="392800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">(請對我報以微笑吧)</p>
<p begin="393600000t" end="454000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(滿腦子心心念念的都是你啊)</p>
<p begin="479200000t" end="517600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(打破冰封三尺的明日吧)</p>
<p begin="518400000t" end="558000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">(盡是些絕對不能失去的事物)</p>
<p begin="558800000t" end="598000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">(我在命運指引的前路上找到了你)</p>
<p begin="598800000t" end="636800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">(如今眼淚已再也沒有意義)</p>
<p begin="637600000t" end="676800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(在飛快地運轉的世界一角)</p>
<p begin="677600000t" end="718400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(有如吶喊一樣呼吸著)</p>
<p begin="719200000t" end="757600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(如能在跨越千千萬萬時光後重逢)</p>
<p begin="758400000t" end="803200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(就在絕望的前方一步笑吧)</p>
<p begin="934600000t" end="962600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">為何鬼族也會來救我們</p>
<p begin="971800000t" end="988200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">為何還會給我們食物</p>
<p begin="1034200000t" end="1052200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">其他人呢？在哪裡</p>
<p begin="1058200000t" end="1087800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">你說食物已經準備好？難道…</p>
<p begin="1136600000t" end="1183400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">穆吉卡，你跑到哪裡？又迷路了嗎</p>
<p begin="1186600000t" end="1206600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">所以你就過來接我們嗎</p>
<p begin="1207400000t" end="1224200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">似乎時機不太好</p>
<p begin="1225000000t" end="1239400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">還拿著那些東西</p>
<p begin="1240200000t" end="1250600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">不然怎樣</p>
<p begin="1251400000t" end="1273400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">如果小孩不小心碰到就糟糕了</p>
<p begin="1274200000t" end="1288200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">實在太危險了</p>
<p begin="1298200000t" end="1326200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">小孩，你沒事吧？臉色很差</p>
<p begin="1327000000t" end="1343400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">其他小孩現時在哪裡</p>
<p begin="1409800000t" end="1419400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="1440600000t" end="1458200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">去到盡頭就轉左</p>
<p begin="1486600000t" end="1498200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">鬼嗎</p>
<p begin="1511400000t" end="1534200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">曾經有人這樣稱呼我</p>
<p begin="1571800000t" end="1581400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">你們…</p>
<p begin="1599800000t" end="1619400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">艾瑪、雷…</p>
<p begin="1659000000t" end="1687000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">實在太好了，艾瑪的病痊癒了</p>
<p begin="1687800000t" end="1702200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">她還沒康復的</p>
<p begin="1704200000t" end="1725000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">大家沒事吧　　是</p>
<p begin="1739000000t" end="1759800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">真的對不起，嚇壞你們</p>
<p begin="1764200000t" end="1796600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">其實我倆真的沒想過傷害你們</p>
<p begin="1812600000t" end="1840600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">我名叫穆吉卡，他名叫孫居</p>
<p begin="1841400000t" end="1864200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">我和他都不吃人類</p>
<p begin="1867400000t" end="1883400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">所以你們可以放心</p>
<p begin="1884200000t" end="1904200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">我們絕對不會傷害你們</p>
<p begin="1951400000t" end="1967400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">來，給你吃吧　　怎麼會這樣</p>
<p begin="1968200000t" end="1984600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">他們好像已經很熟絡</p>
<p begin="2003400000t" end="2023400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">給雷的　　給艾瑪的</p>
<p begin="2047400000t" end="2061000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">剛才一起吃過午餐</p>
<p begin="2061800000t" end="2075400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">甚麼事都沒有發生</p>
<p begin="2076200000t" end="2104200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">如果存心害我們，我們早就沒命了</p>
<p begin="2105000000t" end="2124200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">坦白說，對我們來說</p>
<p begin="2125000000t" end="2153000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">最重要的是他們救了艾瑪和雷</p>
<p begin="2155400000t" end="2176600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">他們是恩人，值得信任的</p>
<p begin="2189800000t" end="2219000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">大家都分到了吧　　對…</p>
<p begin="2251000000t" end="2275400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">我們都獲賜潔淨食糧</p>
<p begin="2276200000t" end="2298200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">值得我們心存感恩之心</p>
<p begin="2300600000t" end="2327000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">大家一起向天地萬物表達謝意</p>
<p begin="2339000000t" end="2353400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">感謝賜予食物…</p>
<p begin="2354200000t" end="2370200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">感謝賜予食物…</p>
<p begin="2396600000t" end="2421000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">感謝賜予食物…</p>
<p begin="2511000000t" end="2522600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">很美味</p>
<p begin="2588600000t" end="2607000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">你倆還沒睡覺嗎</p>
<p begin="2628200000t" end="2661400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">請問方便嗎　　沒問題</p>
<p begin="2735000000t" end="2747000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">很對不起</p>
<p begin="2760200000t" end="2785400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">我沒想過有不吃人類的鬼族</p>
<p begin="2789800000t" end="2808200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">你們剛才救了我們所有人</p>
<p begin="2809000000t" end="2824600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">還要被我們懷疑</p>
<p begin="2825800000t" end="2839000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">別放在心上</p>
<p begin="2839800000t" end="2863800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">你們懷疑我們絕對是正確的</p>
<p begin="2864600000t" end="2885800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">對鬼來說，人肉特別美味</p>
<p begin="2886600000t" end="2901000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">尤其是人腦</p>
<p begin="2903000000t" end="2917800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">大部分鬼看到人類</p>
<p begin="2918600000t" end="2936600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">就會馬上撲過去咬</p>
<p begin="2941800000t" end="2961000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">你全都當作敵人就對了</p>
<p begin="2965400000t" end="2988200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">那麼為何你倆不吃我們</p>
<p begin="2989400000t" end="3003400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">是因為信仰</p>
<p begin="3021000000t" end="3052200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">我們為了信仰，所以決定不吃人類</p>
<p begin="3059800000t" end="3075000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">但只限於人類</p>
<p begin="3080200000t" end="3099800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">人類以外，甚麼都吃</p>
<p begin="3113400000t" end="3133400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">我們就是所謂的社會異類</p>
<p begin="3139400000t" end="3165000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">農場那邊，他們的利益及權威</p>
<p begin="3165800000t" end="3182600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">我們完全不關心</p>
<p begin="3191800000t" end="3219800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">所以救你們，我只是為了興趣</p>
<p begin="3223800000t" end="3244200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">因為我已經很久沒有跟人類</p>
<p begin="3245000000t" end="3260200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">這樣交談過了</p>
<p begin="3271800000t" end="3290600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">現時仍然生存的人類</p>
<p begin="3291400000t" end="3315800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">就只剩下農場裡面那些</p>
<p begin="3347000000t" end="3365400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">你是來問這件事的嗎</p>
<p begin="3384600000t" end="3398600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">請你告訴我們</p>
<p begin="3407000000t" end="3435400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">30年前，人類發生甚麼事</p>
<p begin="3443400000t" end="3473000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">世界現在變成怎樣</p>
<p begin="3480200000t" end="3497400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">其實甚麼都沒有發生</p>
<p begin="3507400000t" end="3519400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">雖然我不知道</p>
<p begin="3520200000t" end="3547400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">你如何得出「30年前」這個數字</p>
<p begin="3548200000t" end="3573800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">但世界在很早之前已經是這樣</p>
<p begin="3577800000t" end="3585800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">這是甚麼意思</p>
<p begin="3586600000t" end="3607400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">難道這裡根本不是地球</p>
<p begin="3613800000t" end="3629000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">這裡是另一個行星</p>
<p begin="3629800000t" end="3646200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">所以才有如此奇怪的生物嗎</p>
<p begin="3647000000t" end="3668200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">不是　　還是日曆是假的？</p>
<p begin="3669000000t" end="3687800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">現在不是2046年，而是…</p>
<p begin="3688600000t" end="3699000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">聽我說</p>
<p begin="3701000000t" end="3711400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">這裡是地球</p>
<p begin="3712200000t" end="3733400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">現在也的確是2046年</p>
<p begin="3741400000t" end="3760600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">是人類的其中一個曆法</p>
<p begin="3761400000t" end="3772200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">那麼…</p>
<p begin="3780200000t" end="3806200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">好吧，讓我告訴你們以前的事</p>
<p begin="3807000000t" end="3823000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">你說以前的事？</p>
<p begin="3877400000t" end="3903400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">以前的世界比現在更加廣闊</p>
<p begin="3909000000t" end="3927000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">在那個廣闊的世界裡</p>
<p begin="3927800000t" end="3959400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">鬼族要靠捕獵大量人類食用來生存</p>
<p begin="3966600000t" end="3989800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">捕食者和被捕食者並存</p>
<p begin="3993000000t" end="4018600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">有些人類怕鬼族，所以不敢反抗</p>
<p begin="4019400000t" end="4034200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">也有憎恨鬼族的人類</p>
<p begin="4035000000t" end="4050600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">反過來獵殺他們</p>
<p begin="4061000000t" end="4070200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">被殺的鬼族</p>
<p begin="4071000000t" end="4094200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">數量還要比鬼族吃掉的人類多</p>
<p begin="4098200000t" end="4125000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">於是鬼族從那時候開始憎恨人類</p>
<p begin="4132200000t" end="4163800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">無盡的殺戮、無盡的恐怖</p>
<p begin="4165400000t" end="4185000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">直到雙方都厭倦了</p>
<p begin="4185800000t" end="4213400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">在那個時候，人類提出一個建議</p>
<p begin="4231800000t" end="4249800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">就是大家做一個約定</p>
<p begin="4253000000t" end="4273000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">人類不再獵殺鬼族</p>
<p begin="4274600000t" end="4293000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">鬼族也不再捕食人類</p>
<p begin="4297400000t" end="4317800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">雙方將這個世界瓜分</p>
<p begin="4326600000t" end="4360600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">這一切就是從這個約定開始</p>
<p begin="4366200000t" end="4391400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">就是這樣，世界從此一分為二</p>
<p begin="4392200000t" end="4406600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">大家斷絕來往</p>
<p begin="4408200000t" end="4438600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">這裡就是當時劃分出來的鬼族世界</p>
<p begin="4449000000t" end="4460600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">換句話說</p>
<p begin="4461400000t" end="4482600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">你們這群食用兒童的祖先</p>
<p begin="4483800000t" end="4518600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">就是當時作為禮物被放置在這裡</p>
<p begin="4523000000t" end="4535000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">放置在這裡？</p>
<p begin="4539000000t" end="4555400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">鬼族不再獵殺人類</p>
<p begin="4557400000t" end="4573000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">為了遵守這個約定</p>
<p begin="4573800000t" end="4582200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">一直以來</p>
<p begin="4583000000t" end="4606200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">我們都是有系統地養殖人類</p>
<p begin="4608200000t" end="4632200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">那些養殖機構稱為「農場」</p>
<p begin="4634200000t" end="4653800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">而恩典農場之家就是</p>
<p begin="4654600000t" end="4677000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">其中一間最高級的農場</p>
<p begin="4677800000t" end="4703000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">是眾多農場中最好的</p>
<p begin="4712200000t" end="4735000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">自從約定以來，過了1000年</p>
<p begin="4739400000t" end="4760600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">世界幾乎沒有改變過</p>
<p begin="4801800000t" end="4813800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">兩個世界？</p>
<p begin="4817000000t" end="4845000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">約定？鬼族跟人類？</p>
<p begin="4877800000t" end="4901800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">太好了…</p>
<p begin="4918600000t" end="4928200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">雖然有點麻煩</p>
<p begin="4929000000t" end="4949000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">但總算可以看到未來</p>
<p begin="4949800000t" end="4970600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">對，比想像中更好</p>
<p begin="4971400000t" end="4992200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">外面還有一個人類的世界</p>
<p begin="4993000000t" end="5020200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">有一個完全沒有任何鬼族的世界</p>
<p begin="5021000000t" end="5035000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">太好了…</p>
<p begin="5035800000t" end="5061000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">不過我還有壞消息要說　　很開心</p>
<p begin="5068200000t" end="5091400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">你們不可以去人類的世界</p>
<p begin="5092200000t" end="5116200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">為甚麼　　因為雙方有約定</p>
<p begin="5121000000t" end="5137400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">達成協議後1000年</p>
<p begin="5138200000t" end="5162200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">都沒有人在兩個世界之間來往過</p>
<p begin="5162990000t" end="5183400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">那你又怎麼知道沒有</p>
<p begin="5186200000t" end="5203800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">這方面只是聽說過</p>
<p begin="5204600000t" end="5229400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">但人類世界的確存在嗎</p>
<p begin="5231790000t" end="5250200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">對，聽說是的</p>
<p begin="5251000000t" end="5275000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">那就沒問題，一定會找到</p>
<p begin="5275800000t" end="5288600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">至於路徑和地點</p>
<p begin="5289400000t" end="5307000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">只要去找就一定能找到</p>
<p begin="5347800000t" end="5358200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">謝謝你，孫居</p>
<p begin="5359000000t" end="5370600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">我精神抖擻了</p>
<p begin="5377000000t" end="5404600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">是嗎？那就太好了</p>
<p begin="5407800000t" end="5430600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">現在時候不早了，回去睡覺吧</p>
<p begin="5441400000t" end="5462600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">明天教你們如何走出這個森林</p>
<p begin="5474200000t" end="5494200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">我會安全地送你們到出口</p>
<p begin="5495000000t" end="5519400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">很感謝你，晚安，孫居</p>
<p begin="5673800000t" end="5699800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">不用擔心，沒有人知道這條路</p>
<p begin="5700600000t" end="5724200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我用枯死的樹木形成的地下通道</p>
<p begin="5725000000t" end="5749400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">將它們連接起來建成通道</p>
<p begin="5750200000t" end="5763800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">在裡面很容易迷路</p>
<p begin="5764600000t" end="5782600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">只有我和穆吉卡知道出入口</p>
<p begin="5783400000t" end="5798200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">我也會迷路</p>
<p begin="5813800000t" end="5829800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">暫時還很順利　　是</p>
<p begin="5830600000t" end="5859000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">農場那群人不熟悉這個森林</p>
<p begin="5865000000t" end="5885400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">這樣穿過森林就最好了</p>
<p begin="5895800000t" end="5916600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">穆吉卡，你住在森林裡嗎</p>
<p begin="5917400000t" end="5948200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">我們居無定所，喜歡四處跑</p>
<p begin="5949000000t" end="5969800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">去過很多不同的地方</p>
<p begin="5975400000t" end="6005000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">是含有水分的海葵　　說得沒錯</p>
<p begin="6011400000t" end="6033000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">前面就是它們生長的地方</p>
<p begin="6033800000t" end="6062200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">大家在那裡休息吧　　好…</p>
<p begin="6088600000t" end="6121000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">1000年前，人類跟鬼族的約定？</p>
<p begin="6128200000t" end="6157400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">所謂約定，原來就是這個意思</p>
<p begin="6160200000t" end="6186200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">而一直以來，書本上說的世界</p>
<p begin="6187000000t" end="6203800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">原來不是這裡嗎</p>
<p begin="6207800000t" end="6222200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">而且這種農場</p>
<p begin="6223000000t" end="6243800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">不是只有恩典農場之家</p>
<p begin="6244600000t" end="6265400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">還有很多　　真的嗎</p>
<p begin="6271800000t" end="6284600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">實在太可怕了</p>
<p begin="6285400000t" end="6308200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">那麼我們就去救其他人吧</p>
<p begin="6317800000t" end="6346600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">所以才要找米涅瓦先生</p>
<p begin="6347400000t" end="6369800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">向他請教去人類世界的方法</p>
<p begin="6373800000t" end="6395000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">待一切都準備妥當之後</p>
<p begin="6395800000t" end="6431400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">就趕去救菲爾和其他孤兒院的小孩</p>
<p begin="6436200000t" end="6463400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">然後大家就一起去人類的世界</p>
<p begin="6496200000t" end="6515000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">這麼容易就能做到嗎</p>
<p begin="6525400000t" end="6558600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">我們光是逃走出來已經不容易了</p>
<p begin="6563800000t" end="6575400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">說得也是</p>
<p begin="6583400000t" end="6607400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">我也覺得這不是一件容易的事</p>
<p begin="6611800000t" end="6643000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">不過，總算有一個希望</p>
<p begin="6645400000t" end="6662600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">暫時只可以見步行步</p>
<p begin="6663400000t" end="6689800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">雖然沒有其他辦法，但也看到前路</p>
<p begin="6695800000t" end="6709400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">一個都不能死</p>
<p begin="6710600000t" end="6727000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">大家要一起生存下去</p>
<p begin="6730200000t" end="6748200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">大家要一起笑</p>
<p begin="6750600000t" end="6767800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">既然我們已經看到前路</p>
<p begin="6768600000t" end="6779400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">無論做甚麼</p>
<p begin="6780200000t" end="6796600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">無論多困難、多危險</p>
<p begin="6797400000t" end="6807400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">都不用害怕</p>
<p begin="6819400000t" end="6857000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">沒錯，我們要繼續逃走　　好…</p>
<p begin="6884200000t" end="6895400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">原來如此</p>
<p begin="6896200000t" end="6927800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">你們的目的地是想去東南方</p>
<p begin="6932200000t" end="6951800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">那麼就從森林的北面出去</p>
<p begin="6952600000t" end="6966200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">然後再回頭</p>
<p begin="6969000000t" end="6976200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">從北面出去？</p>
<p begin="6977000000t" end="6995400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">如果從這裡向東南方走</p>
<p begin="6996200000t" end="7007000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">出了森林之後</p>
<p begin="7007800000t" end="7024600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">就會是鬼族的領地</p>
<p begin="7034200000t" end="7066600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">但如果從北面去，沿途只有荒野</p>
<p begin="7067400000t" end="7075800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">雖然走遠了</p>
<p begin="7076600000t" end="7097400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">但最多五天就能穿過森林</p>
<p begin="7103400000t" end="7114600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">之後再步行一天</p>
<p begin="7115400000t" end="7134200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">就會到達你們的目的地</p>
<p begin="7140600000t" end="7165000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">趁這個時候，讓你們多學一些東西</p>
<p begin="7173800000t" end="7191000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">我和穆吉卡會教你們</p>
<p begin="7195000000t" end="7214200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">在外面世界生存</p>
<p begin="7216600000t" end="7246600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">最基本的知識和技術</p>
<p begin="7315000000t" end="7328200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">謝謝你，安娜</p>
<p begin="7330200000t" end="7349800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">艾瑪，有時間嗎</p>
<p begin="7356600000t" end="7380200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">其實我昨天就想跟你說一件事</p>
<p begin="7381000000t" end="7411000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">但一直都沒有機會　　甚麼事</p>
<p begin="7421400000t" end="7449400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">就是你不舒服就應該早點說</p>
<p begin="7450200000t" end="7463400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="7468200000t" end="7497400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">聽我說，你別再勉強捱下去</p>
<p begin="7498200000t" end="7529400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">絕對不可以，知道嗎</p>
<p begin="7542200000t" end="7551800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">知道</p>
<p begin="7555800000t" end="7569400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">知…知道了</p>
<p begin="7570200000t" end="7594600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">艾瑪，你知道不可以這樣胡來嗎</p>
<p begin="7595400000t" end="7620200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">計劃中根本沒有割下耳朵這個部分</p>
<p begin="7621000000t" end="7634200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">雖然你很勇敢</p>
<p begin="7635000000t" end="7647000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">但如果死了的話</p>
<p begin="7647800000t" end="7661000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">那就甚麼都沒有了</p>
<p begin="7662600000t" end="7682600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">對不起，不過…</p>
<p begin="7687800000t" end="7703000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">別再說「不過」</p>
<p begin="7715000000t" end="7733000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">對不起　　被人罵了…</p>
<p begin="7733800000t" end="7745800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">你也要捱罵</p>
<p begin="7747000000t" end="7761800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">聽說你拿自己當誘餌</p>
<p begin="7762600000t" end="7777000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">你想一個人對付那些</p>
<p begin="7777800000t" end="7793800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">像蜥蜴般的鬼族</p>
<p begin="7795000000t" end="7811400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">跟鬼族玩捉迷藏，你傻了嗎</p>
<p begin="7812200000t" end="7820600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">還是瘋了？</p>
<p begin="7821400000t" end="7849400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">一不小心，很容易性命不保的</p>
<p begin="7850200000t" end="7859000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">太過分了</p>
<p begin="7859800000t" end="7875800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">說夠了嗎？我只是…</p>
<p begin="7876600000t" end="7899800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">別吵了，不如問問孫居吧</p>
<p begin="7900600000t" end="7917000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">這樣是百分之百會死的</p>
<p begin="7917800000t" end="7937800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">聽到了嗎　　才不是</p>
<p begin="7938600000t" end="7965000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">不要，你別死</p>
<p begin="7985000000t" end="8011800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">我不會死…　　弄哭了她</p>
<p begin="8012600000t" end="8043000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">雷，我很擔心你</p>
<p begin="8055800000t" end="8079800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">艾瑪，我真的很擔心你</p>
<p begin="8084600000t" end="8115800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">你甚麼都沒說，就突然暈倒了</p>
<p begin="8116600000t" end="8126600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="8127400000t" end="8160200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">我們知道艾瑪和雷經常擔心我們</p>
<p begin="8161000000t" end="8187400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">現在輪到我們擔心你們了</p>
<p begin="8188200000t" end="8221000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">對，唐幾乎哭出來了　　甚麼</p>
<p begin="8224200000t" end="8244600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">如果需要幫忙，就說出來吧</p>
<p begin="8246600000t" end="8265800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">如果覺得辛苦就別勉強</p>
<p begin="8269800000t" end="8302200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">就當我拜託你，你自己必須小心</p>
<p begin="8305800000t" end="8319000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">總之艾瑪和雷</p>
<p begin="8319800000t" end="8345800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">在我們心目中，就等於家人</p>
<p begin="8349000000t" end="8384600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">我們會努力幫你們，甚麼都願意做</p>
<p begin="8388600000t" end="8415400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">有甚麼事就儘管說吧</p>
<p begin="8418200000t" end="8429800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">我會的</p>
<p begin="8435800000t" end="8448200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">很感謝你</p>
<p begin="8450200000t" end="8459400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">對不起</p>
<p begin="8469400000t" end="8484200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">對不起，各位</p>
<p begin="8599800000t" end="8629400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">很美味，這是甚麼　　食物</p>
<p begin="8630200000t" end="8642200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">我也知道是食物</p>
<p begin="8643000000t" end="8664200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">這麼美味的食物是怎麼煮出來的</p>
<p begin="8665000000t" end="8694600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">我只是按照穆吉卡教我的方法去煮</p>
<p begin="8695400000t" end="8724600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">怎麼可能？味道和份量都適中</p>
<p begin="8725400000t" end="8736200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">因為我是一個天才</p>
<p begin="8737000000t" end="8747800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">我不相信</p>
<p begin="8748600000t" end="8767400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">我們是負責起火的</p>
<p begin="8768200000t" end="8792200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">我壓碎番薯　　我揉成一顆顆</p>
<p begin="8793000000t" end="8823400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">大家雖然第一次做，但做得很好</p>
<p begin="8839400000t" end="8871800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">來，大家先坐下來吧　　是…</p>
<p begin="8883800000t" end="8897000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">我們開始吃了…</p>
<p begin="8933800000t" end="8944600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">怎麼了</p>
<p begin="8953800000t" end="8961800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">沒事</p>
<p begin="8969800000t" end="9002600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">吃到美味的食物，我覺得很幸福</p>
<p begin="9490600000t" end="9508200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">艾瑪，準備</p>
<p begin="9544600000t" end="9565800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">厲害…</p>
<p begin="9575000000t" end="9585000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">孫居？</p>
<p begin="9587800000t" end="9604600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">我先去看看情況</p>
<p begin="9607000000t" end="9624200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">然後我們就要上地面</p>
<p begin="9625000000t" end="9640600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">要渡過河流</p>
<p begin="9644200000t" end="9659000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">你要小心點</p>
<p begin="9665400000t" end="9675400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">孫居</p>
<p begin="9683000000t" end="9704600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">求求你帶我一起去吧，行嗎</p>
<p begin="9706600000t" end="9726200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">我很想看看外面的世界</p>
<p begin="9735000000t" end="9745400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">沒問題</p>
<p begin="9746200000t" end="9771800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">不過你絕對不可以離開我的身邊</p>
<p begin="9947800000t" end="9973800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">這條河的水很淺，而且有點冷</p>
<p begin="9974600000t" end="9990600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">但應該也能走過去</p>
<p begin="9995400000t" end="10012600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">只怕那些追捕鬼</p>
<p begin="10044600000t" end="10067400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">幸好不是　　這樣就對了</p>
<p begin="10069800000t" end="10085400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">經常要提高警覺</p>
<p begin="10086200000t" end="10103800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">觀察是否有敵人埋伏</p>
<p begin="10104600000t" end="10122200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">如果有，就要想辦法逃走</p>
<p begin="10127000000t" end="10157000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">我明白了，一邊觀察，一邊思考</p>
<p begin="10215400000t" end="10238600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">我想知道你的目的是甚麼</p>
<p begin="10249400000t" end="10266600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">估計你應該不是貪玩</p>
<p begin="10267400000t" end="10287400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">所以才跟著我出來看</p>
<p begin="10299000000t" end="10323800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">我想你教我…　　甚麼</p>
<p begin="10331400000t" end="10347800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">教我殺生的方法</p>
<p begin="10360200000t" end="10393000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">這幾天，你分別教導我們如何做飯</p>
<p begin="10393800000t" end="10410990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">如何分辨植物的知識</p>
<p begin="10412200000t" end="10425400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">以及如何製藥</p>
<p begin="10426190000t" end="10448190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">還有就是弓和箭的用法</p>
<p begin="10452200000t" end="10481800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">不過你還沒教導我如何捕獵</p>
<p begin="10489400000t" end="10505400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">我想在我們分開之前</p>
<p begin="10506600000t" end="10524200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">你可以教導我更多東西</p>
<p begin="10529000000t" end="10554200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">肉類、魚類、蔬菜和水果</p>
<p begin="10557400000t" end="10567400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">所有東西</p>
<p begin="10568200000t" end="10593400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">以後我們都要靠自己雙手找回來</p>
<p begin="10594200000t" end="10609800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">然後將它們變成食物</p>
<p begin="10618600000t" end="10644200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">如何捕捉動物食用的方法</p>
<p begin="10654200000t" end="10674600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">以及如何狩獵都請你教我</p>
<p begin="10867000000t" end="10893000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">如果不戰鬥，就沒辦法守護人類</p>
<p begin="10893800000t" end="10915800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">包括你朋友和你自己</p>
<p begin="11147800000t" end="11166600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">很溫暖，還有生命</p>
<p begin="11167400000t" end="11193000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">你的箭法不錯，接著就是儀程</p>
<p begin="11193800000t" end="11203800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">儀程？</p>
<p begin="11219000000t" end="11229000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">這些是…</p>
<p begin="11239400000t" end="11251400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">小心拿著它</p>
<p begin="11252200000t" end="11273000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">這是名為維達的吸血植物</p>
<p begin="11275000000t" end="11291800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">將它插在獵物的胸口</p>
<p begin="11311400000t" end="11330600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">要將糧食奉獻給神</p>
<p begin="11331400000t" end="11356200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">如果神願意接受，那花朵就會開</p>
<p begin="11357000000t" end="11378200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">這個時候就可以吃牠的肉</p>
<p begin="11381400000t" end="11395400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">這就稱為儀程</p>
<p begin="11396200000t" end="11418600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">也是我們傳統的屠宰方法</p>
<p begin="11422600000t" end="11439800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">這樣可以抽掉血水</p>
<p begin="11441800000t" end="11463000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">令肉類能保存得更久</p>
<p begin="11482200000t" end="11501800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">趁牠還有體溫就插進去？</p>
<p begin="11502600000t" end="11520600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">這樣才能把血抽出來</p>
<p begin="11526200000t" end="11534600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">不要緊</p>
<p begin="11535400000t" end="11558200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">牠已經斷氣了，不會覺得痛</p>
<p begin="11611800000t" end="11624200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">想放棄嗎</p>
<p begin="11693000000t" end="11718600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">我們不想被鬼族吃掉，想生存</p>
<p begin="11719400000t" end="11742200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">因此，我們需要食物</p>
<p begin="11743400000t" end="11753800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">如果不吃東西</p>
<p begin="11754600000t" end="11775000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">我們就沒辦法生存下去</p>
<p begin="12004600000t" end="12037400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">這朵花曾經插在妹妹的胸口上</p>
<p begin="12041400000t" end="12054200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">你曾經見過嗎</p>
<p begin="12077800000t" end="12115400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">要趁還有體溫，然後插進去</p>
<p begin="12127800000t" end="12162200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">柯妮、豪、賽蒂</p>
<p begin="12173400000t" end="12181800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">諾曼</p>
<p begin="12191400000t" end="12212600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">希望你們不會覺得痛吧</p>
<p begin="12219000000t" end="12243000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">希望你們當時不覺得恐懼</p>
<p begin="12252200000t" end="12273800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">儀程是要向神表示感謝</p>
<p begin="12277000000t" end="12297000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">要有恭敬之心才能成立</p>
<p begin="12306600000t" end="12318600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">你可以安心</p>
<p begin="12320200000t" end="12341800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">我相信你們的兄弟姐妹</p>
<p begin="12344200000t" end="12365000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">一定不會感到痛苦</p>
<p begin="12511000000t" end="12525800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">謝謝你，孫居</p>
<p begin="12574600000t" end="12616200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">艾瑪，你回來就好了…</p>
<p begin="12641800000t" end="12663400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">太好了…</p>
<p begin="12669400000t" end="12691400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">艾瑪，你怎麼了</p>
<p begin="12693400000t" end="12717800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">發生甚麼事？你沒事吧</p>
<p begin="12732200000t" end="12742600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">沒甚麼</p>
<p begin="12773400000t" end="12785400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">我沒事</p>
<p begin="12831400000t" end="12857800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">(當你許下願望)</p>
<p begin="12858600000t" end="12885000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">(月亮就灑下了影子)</p>
<p begin="12885800000t" end="12941800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">(像魔法一般的夜晚必定融化無蹤)</p>
<p begin="13049800000t" end="13076200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">(以澄澈響亮的聲音)</p>
<p begin="13077000000t" end="13103400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">(風宣布了夜色來臨)</p>
<p begin="13104200000t" end="13130600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">(藍色世界的一切)</p>
<p begin="13131400000t" end="13158200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">(都在童話裡沉睡)</p>
<p begin="13159000000t" end="13185000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">(你在半夢半醒之間)</p>
<p begin="13185800000t" end="13211800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">(張開了閉著的眼瞼)</p>
<p begin="13212600000t" end="13237000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">(比我心裡所想的)</p>
<p begin="13237800000t" end="13273400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">(還要更加朦朧)</p>
<p begin="13289800000t" end="13338200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">(如果這聲音能傳達)</p>
<p begin="13339000000t" end="13365000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">(即使得不到回應　也想在你身旁)</p>
<p begin="13365800000t" end="13397400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">(不想讓這個故事畫下句點)</p>
<p begin="13398200000t" end="13447000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">(跨越長夜而去吧)</p>
<p begin="13447800000t" end="13473000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">(跟你在一起　就再也不需要言語)</p>
<p begin="13473800000t" end="13520200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">(如今只想確認彼此的溫度)</p>
<p begin="13521000000t" end="13556200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">(讓我沉入不會醒的美夢吧)</p>
<p begin="13557000000t" end="13603000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">(我們緊握著那雙手)</p>
<p begin="13603800000t" end="13632600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">(靜靜地祈願著)</p>
</div>
